item.title: Patch Notes | 1.19 Pre-Release 5
item.description: Patch Notes | 1.19 Pre-Release 5 1.19 Pre-Release 5 We’ve now released pre-release 5 to fix a few more bugs. Fixed Bugs MC-249121 - Sculk is missing subtitles for some sounds. MC-249323 - Modifying a world preset to not include overworld settings will not give a datapack error, but selecting the world type will instantly crash your game. MC-250034 - Standing on top of mud as it converts to clay causes the player to fall through or be pushed out of the block.
